TopicTitle: Munanigans: To the Mun by Space Shuttle, Return by EVA (HD)

Articles.Content:
Hello, world! I'm glad to be back on the KSP forums!

My first KSP video, about an awesome mission I flew this weekend to the Mun.

I hope to go on a (mis)adventure every week. I've even got a nice microphone I want to try out.
